249
00:17:03,409 --> 00:17:04,577
<i>Kau baik-baik saja?</i>

250
00:17:05,077 --> 00:17:06,745
<i>Kau pasti kaget malam itu.</i>

251
00:17:11,375 --> 00:17:13,335
<i>Aku ingin beri tahu aku sudah pulih.</i>

252
00:17:17,798 --> 00:17:21,468
