254
00:17:29,518 --> 00:17:31,812
<i>Mulai saat itu, aku berhenti minum.</i>

255
00:17:33,856 --> 00:17:36,817
<i>Jadi, tolong maafkan aku.</i>

256
00:17:40,904 --> 00:17:43,282
