288
00:19:57,916 --> 00:20:00,711
Aku ambil cuti karenamu.

289
00:20:00,794 --> 00:20:03,213
Kubilang kirim surel. Kenapa kau begini?

290
00:20:03,672 --> 00:20:05,174
Kau menggangguku sepanjang hari.

291
00:20:05,257 --> 00:20:08,886
Aku bersalah, harus kuperbaiki.

292
00:20:09,595 --> 00:20:12,598
