308
00:21:04,066 --> 00:21:05,108
Dia mengabaikanku.

309
00:21:09,404 --> 00:21:10,656
<i>Pak Cha.</i>

310
00:21:10,906 --> 00:21:13,617
<i>Aku sudah minta maaf pada Pak Ji.</i>

311
00:21:14,076 --> 00:21:15,536
<i>Dia tak marah lagi padaku.</i>

312
00:21:16,870 --> 00:21:19,414
<i>Mulai kini, akan kupisahkan
kerja dan kehidupan pribadi.</i>

313
00:21:23,585 --> 00:21:24,628
Aku lapar.

