345
00:22:43,123 --> 00:22:46,418
Aku yakin suatu saat nanti
dia muncul membawa <i>Para Pahlawan</i>.

346
00:22:47,002 --> 00:22:49,379
Saat semua orang tak menduga,

347
00:22:49,796 --> 00:22:51,798
dia muncul dengan karya hebat

348
00:22:51,882 --> 00:22:54,718
